data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER! Gorgeous and conveniently located home in the Westchester community in Grand Prairie. A great layout that provides the perfect space for hosting family and friends. The first floor features the large master retreat with updated shower, dual sinks and walk in closet, family room with a cozy fireplace that opens to the kitchen with plenty of cabinets for storage, breakfast nook, separate dining room, formal living, office room, laundry and half bathroom. Upstairs you will find a bonus flex space area, 4 additional bedrooms and 1 full bath. Enjoy the convenience of a 2 car attached garage. It's close to major highways and local amenities such as shopping and restaurants. With its very functional layout, this house is sure to make you feel right at home! Don't miss your chance to own this lovely property!
